NEW Farmacy Daily Greens Moisturizer
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
guys... I have been anxiously waiting for today! @farmacybeauty daily greens oil free gel moisturizer is out now at sephora and i’ve partnered with them to bring you first impressions✨ I filmed this video the first day I tried it over a week ago, and still feel the exact same way.

made for combo/oily skin types, it’s an absolute dream for me. it reduces shine, helps keeps pores clear, yet keeps my skin SUPER supple and bouncy. oh, and it has the most amazing uplifting scent that I’m obsessed with. if you’re dry, this would be a great layering product for more hydration, but i definitely see this geared more toward oilier skin.

watch the video for more info on ingredients! for $38 and 1.7oz, it’s a steep price but definitely worth picking up at the sephora sale starting this week 😘 plus, a little goes a LONG way!
